pulltitle: Update fill command to load files from s3 (bug 1196817)
pullsbody:
This would require the mozilla path to be a S3 URL. E.g.:

`./manage.py fill users --mozilla s3://private-bucket/shared_storage/dumped-users/tarballs/2015-08-25.tgz`
